960&ff=20240409140941&v=2.18.0.post9+e462414">38585275</a> | PMC： <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/PMC10995313/?utm_source=Chrome&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=journals&utm_content=101560960&ff=20240409140941&v=2.18.0.post9+e462414">PMC10995313</a> | DOI： <a href=https://doi.org/10.3389/fimmu.2024.1368142>10.3389/fimmu.2024.1368142</a></p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><guid ispermalink="false">发布：38585275</guid><pubDate> Mon, 08 Apr 2024 06:00:00 -0400</pubDate><dc:creator>凯蒂纪念日</dc:creator><dc:creator>卢卡斯·伦佩尔</dc:creator><dc:creator>法比奥·MV·罗西</dc:creator><dc:creator>海军陆战队特雷特</dc:creator><dc:date>2024-04-08</dc:date><dc:source>免疫学前沿</dc:source><dc:title>两种非粘膜组织中嗜酸性粒细胞的起源和功能</dc:title><dc:identifier>下午:38585275</dc:identifier><dc:identifier>管理中心：PMC10995313</dc:identifier><dc:identifier> doi:10.3389/fimmu.2024.1368142</dc:identifier></item><item><title>社论：腹足动物免疫和宿主-病原体相互作用</title><link/>https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/38585274/?utm_source=Chrome&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=journals&amp;utm_content=101560960&amp;fc=None&amp;ff=20240409140941&amp;v=2.18.0.post9+e462414<description>无摘要</description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<div><p style="color: #4aa564;"><b>前沿免疫学</b>。 2024 年 3 月 22 日；15:1385106。 doi：10.3389/fimmu.2024.1385106。电子馆藏 2024。</p><p><b>无摘要</b></p><p style="color: lightgray">PMID： <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/38585274/?utm_source=Chrome&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=journals&utm_content=101560960&ff=20240409140941&v=2.18.0.post9+e462414">38585274</a> | PMC： <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/PMC10995409/?utm_source=Chrome&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=journals&utm_content=101560960&ff=20240409140941&v=2.18.0.post9+e462414">PMC10995409</a> | DOI： <a href=https://doi.org/10.3389/fimmu.2024.1385106>10.3389/fimmu.2024.1385106</a></p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><guid ispermalink="false">发布：38585274</guid><pubDate> Mon, 08 Apr 2024 06:00:00 -0400</pubDate><dc:creator>乔安娜·M·布里杰</dc:creator><dc:creator>马蒂·奈特</dc:creator><dc:date>2024-04-0